title: New & Video: Fthrsn – On Our WAY
content: New material from Fthrsn AND a new video. Wowza, and to think I thought this day wasn’t going to get any better than me sitting in my bed, half naked, eating chicken wings. What a fool I was. But yeah, check the vid; kid sure can dance.
